  "body": "We should define somewhere properly how the storage slots for reentrancy locks are chosen. In the compiler code, we can see this [here](https://github.com/vyperlang/vyper/blob/master/vyper/semantics/analysis/data_positions.py#L98). Also, I feel we should disallow empty reentrancy locks like `@nonreentrant(\"\")` or `@nonreentrant(\" \")` for safety reasons.",
