    "body": "nonreentrant keys are in `-f layout` output format.\r\n```bash\r\n$ vyper -f layout /dev/stdin <<EOF\r\n@external\r\n@nonreentrant(\"x\")\r\ndef foo():\r\n  pass\r\nEOF\r\n{\"storage_layout\": {\"nonreentrant.x\": {\"type\": \"nonreentrant lock\", \"slot\": 0}}, \"code_layout\": {}}\r\n```",
